"Creates symlink from array config file to /etc/snapraid.conf allowing "
"snapraid commands to work on default array without specifying the config "
"file flag"
msgstr "Maakt symlink van array-configbestand naar/etc/snapraid.conf waardoor snapraid commando's kunnen werken op standaard array zonder de configbestand vlag op te geven"

